CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775235955
OL,3,CLocals angered by fly-tipping on
OL,4,Cpopular dog walking route in Somerset
OL,6,FKitty reported the incident to
OL,7,FSomerset Council which is
OL,8,Finvestigating.
OL,10,FKitty said: "It really disappointed me
OL,11,F- the tip is 10 minutes down the road,
OL,12,Fit made me feel really frustrated."
OL,14,FShe added, "The rubbish consisted of
OL,15,Froof tiles, mattresses, kids toys,
OL,16,Ftarpaulin, cabinets among other
OL,17,Fthings."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
