OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775235955
OL,3,CLocals angered by fly-tipping on
OL,4,Cpopular dog walking route in Somerset
OL,6,FSomerset Council said fly-tipping is a
OL,7,F"significant issue" in the county,
OL,8,Fcausing "both environmental damage and
OL,9,Finconvenience to local businesses,
OL,10,Fresidents and tourists".
OL,12,FIt said it the waste was collected by
OL,13,Fits staff on Thursday.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the council said:
OL,16,F"Illegal dumping of waste not only
OL,17,Fspoils the countryside but also poses
OL,18,Fhealth risks and increases the
OL,19,Ffinancial burden on local authorities,
OL,20,Fwho must spend considerable resources
OL,21,Fon clean up and enforcement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
