PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775235955
OL,3,CLocals angered by fly-tipping on
OL,4,Cpopular dog walking route in Somerset
OL,6,F"The persistent nature of fly tipping
OL,7,Fhighlights the need for greater public
OL,8,Fawareness and stronger measures to
OL,9,Fdeter offenders."
OL,11,FThe council has said it wants anyone
OL,12,Fwho witnesses fly-tipping to report
OL,13,Fthe incidents via its website.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
